^59^|^2007-05-09 05:11:35^|^The Clientele @ Black Cat.^|^The first time someone told me about The Clientele five or six years ago, refinement was the selling point. This wasn't you average pop band. This was a following. An exquisite cause that rewarded the discerning few cultivated to appreciate its recordings.

