^69^|^2007-09-07 16:13:42^|^What's the Standard Issue?^|^A ritual stop on my regular tour of DC blogs is <a href="http://www.weeklystandard.com/weblogs/TWSFP/">The Worldwide Standard</a>, an online outpost of the conservative magazine <a href="http://www.weeklystandard.com/default.asp" target="_blank">The Weekly Standard</a>.

