Last month a Times blog posted <a href="http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2008/02/mirthala-salina.html">a Spanish quote from the paper's sister publication</a>, Hoy, and took a little flack for it. So this certainly isn't the first time across this particular ford in the stream.

